Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.43,0:01:20.64,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\bord0\blur0.6\4a&HFF&\c&H30C3F1&}И {\c&HFFFFFF&}тогда {\c&H30C3F1&}все {\c&HFFFFFF&}меня {\c&H30C3F1&}обманули
